! name: ALLYX ONE — On-Device Privacy Tools
! description: Curated by ALLYX ONE (allyxone.com). Surfaces browser-side tools and trusted privacy resources. Demotes services that upload your files to remote servers. Free browser tools. No upload. No account.
! public: true
! author: ALLYX ONE
! homepage: https://allyxone.com
! issues: https://allyxone.com
